bilingual.target: 这款游戏具有惊人的图形的效果。

bilingual.source: The rover sent back stunning images from Mars.
bilingual.target: 探测车从火星发回了惊人的图像。

bilingual.source: Zaragoza is known for its stunning architecture.
bilingual.target: 萨拉戈萨以其惊人的建筑而闻名。

bilingual.source: Guilin is famous for its stunning karst landscape.
bilingual.target: 桂林以其惊人的喀斯特地貌而闻名。

bilingual.source: The artists collaborated to create a stunning mural.
bilingual.target: 艺术家们合作创作了一幅惊人的壁画。

bilingual.source: The artist used metal to create a stunning sculpture.
bilingual.target: 艺术家使用金属创作了一件惊人的雕塑。

bilingual.source: The artist used fusain to create a stunning portrait.
bilingual.target: 艺术家使用木炭创作了一幅惊人的肖像。

bilingual.source: The artist uses metals to create stunning sculptures.
bilingual.target: 这位艺术家使用金属来创作惊人的雕塑。

bilingual.source: The artist painted a stunning snowscape on the canvas.
bilingual.target: 这位艺术家在画布上画了一幅惊人的雪景。

bilingual.source: The ballerina performed a stunning pirouette on stage.
bilingual.target: 芭蕾舞女演员在舞台上表演了一个惊人的旋转。

yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Rise of the Planet of the Apes》

yingyinNormal.en: Wow. Wow. And bam, boom! Absolutely. You look stunning.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哇。惊艳吧，绝对的！你太美了

yingyinNormal.en: He looked at the stunning woman who was his boss and said, "It's murder."
yingyinNormal.zh: 他看着他的头儿眼前这名绝色女子低声说这是谋杀。

yingyinNormal.en: Good. I haven't smoked yet today, I feel great, and confident. That is a stunning blouse.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很有效，我今天还没抽烟，清爽又有自信，好漂亮的上衣。

yingyinNormal.en: And this color is just stunning. It's a peachy nude color perfect to pair with smoky eyes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个颜色看起来好极了。是桃色，与灰色的眼睛很搭配。

yingyinNormal.en: Wanna give me a hand? Sure. Monica, I can't get over how great you look. You look stunning.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你要帮我吗？好，我真的觉得你很漂亮。

yingyinNormal.en: Was he wearing a stunning blue suit? And a power tie? No, pretty much just a towel. Oh, God!
yingyinNormal.zh: 他穿着迷人的蓝色西装？打着领带？不，他只围一条浴巾。上帝呀。

yingyinNormal.en: You mean Jexica. I am Jexica. I have achieved stunning and unheard of popularity. I have everything I want.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说的是杰克西卡。我就是杰克西卡，我现在已经有名到炸裂了，我得到了我想要的一切。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Many of the destinations I visit have <highlight>stunning</highlight> scenery, and I get to meet a variety of people from all over the world.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我参观的许多目的地都有令人惊叹的风景，我可以认识来自世界各地的各种各样的人。

examination_example.sentence: The paintings may yield even more <highlight>stunning</highlight> surprises as additional sections are put together like pieces of a puzzle.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些画可能会产生更多惊人的惊喜，因为额外的部分被拼在一起，就像拼图的碎片。
这些令人惊叹的画面被生动地描绘了出来。

examination_example.sentence: Climate scientists described the phenomenon as "<highlight>stunning</highlight>. "
examination_example.sentence_trans: 气候科学家称这种现象“令人震惊”。

examination_example.sentence: "It was kind of <highlight>stunning</highlight> when she sort of dropped off into oblivion (遗忘)," said Dr. Etheridge.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 埃斯里奇博士说：“当她几乎被人遗忘的时候，这有点令人震惊。”
